data.description: HERE IS YOUR CHANCE! NO GROUND RENT AND CHAP TAX QUALIFIED!  Directly across from Union Square Park with a straight shot to the center gazebo, is this beautiful 4 bedroom and 4 bathroom  historic gem. Find all the assets you could want in this recently renovated home accompanied by 10ft ceilings, 4 car parking pad,  all new LG kitchen appliances, and a large yard for your private outings! Inside then Owner's suit not only will you have an individual cooling system for the room, you'll also find a large bonus space that can be used for home office, lounge, infant bedroom, workout space and more! Several homes on this row have been converted into multi family dwellings and gives you the option for additional income. This property also qualifies for the Healthy Neighborhoods program that could assist in little to no down payment, rates 1% below market rates, with no mortgage insurance,  and potential for a $10,000 matching grant. What else could you ask for! Priced to sell immediately and will not last long!
